@startuml PMA_DFD_Level1
' Personalized Medical Assistant - Data Flow Diagram (Level 1)
' Generated: November 7, 2025
' To use in draw.io: Arrange → Insert → Advanced → PlantUML

title Personalized Medical Assistant - DFD Level 1

' Professional colorful styling - Compact
skinparam backgroundColor #F8F9FA
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontSize 8
skinparam linetype ortho

skinparam rectangle {
    BorderColor #424242
    BorderThickness 2
    FontSize 9
    FontStyle bold
}

skinparam actor {
    BorderColor #424242
    BorderThickness 2
    FontSize 9
    FontStyle bold
}

skinparam database {
    BorderColor #424242
    BorderThickness 2
    FontSize 8
    FontStyle bold
}

skinparam arrow {
    Color #424242
    Thickness 2
    FontSize 7
    FontColor #212121
}

skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FFF9C4
    BorderColor #F57F17
    BorderThickness 2
    FontSize 8
}

' ============ Layout ============
left to right direction

' ============ Top: External Entities ============
actor "Patient" as PAT #90CAF9
actor "Doctor" as DOC #66BB6A

' ============ Middle: Processes ============
rectangle "1.0\nAuthentication" as P1 #81C784
rectangle "2.0\nRecord Mgmt" as P2 #FFB74D
rectangle "3.0\nML Prediction" as P3 #CE93D8
rectangle "4.0\nAppointments" as P4 #EF9A9A
rectangle "5.0\nMessaging" as P5 #80DEEA
rectangle "6.0\nReminders" as P6 #FFA726

' ============ Bottom: Data Stores ============
database "D1: Users" as D1 #4A90E2
database "D2: Records" as D2 #FFB74D
database "D3: Predictions" as D3 #AB47BC
database "D4: Appointments" as D4 #EF5350
database "D5: Messages" as D5 #26C6DA

' ============ Key Data Flows ============

' Patient to System
PAT --> P1
PAT --> P2
PAT --> P3
PAT --> P4

' Doctor to System
DOC --> P1
DOC --> P2
DOC --> P4

' System to Users
P3 --> PAT
P4 --> PAT
P6 --> PAT

P2 --> DOC
P4 --> DOC

' Process to Data Store
P1 --> D1
P2 --> D2
P3 --> D3
P4 --> D4
P5 --> D5

' Inter-Process
P1 --> P2
P2 --> P3
P3 --> P5
P4 --> P5

note right of PAT
**Patient Inputs:**
• Login
• Upload Records
• Enter Symptoms
• Request Appointment
end note

note left of DOC
**Doctor Actions:**
• Login
• Access Records
• Manage Schedule
end note

note bottom of P3
**ML Prediction Process**
Returns disease prediction
and recommendations
end note

@enduml
